                    },
                    "body": "We tested the resolution in the bug description. This fixes the broken oci adapter.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=cmuench",
                        "name": "cmuench",
                        "displayName": "Christian M\u00fcnch",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-02-07T08:04:32.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-02-07T08:04:32.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/19981",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=sunfire",
                        "name": "sunfire",
                        "displayName": "Thorsten Kunz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I wonder why this is not fixed yet? This allows for SQL injection if people use the PDO_OCI adapter and rely on _quote() to work as advertised!\nThe fix is so easy and already accepted in the regular Oracle adapter so please can someone commit the fix?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=sunfire",
                        "name": "sunfire",
                        "displayName": "Thorsten Kunz",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-03-18T09:33:40.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-03-18T09:33:40.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/22792",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rodolfo",
                        "name": "rodolfo",
                        "displayName": "rodolfo",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I have problems like this using Zend_Auth_Adapter_DbTable with Oracle Express and I created a patch to this in  Zend_Db_Adapter_Pdo_Oci.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rodolfo",
                        "name": "rodolfo",
                        "displayName": "rodolfo",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-07-07T11:44:22.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-07-07T11:44:22.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/24803",
                    "author": {
