                        "name": "mikaelkael",
                        "displayName": "Mickael Perraud",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Fixed in SVN11672 (applies same quoting as Oracle adapter).\nFix test failure testSelectColumnWithColonQuotedParameter.",
